{"tid":946615,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"礦難停不了！多款虛擬幣礦機低過一折求售","createTime":"2018-12-18T15:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T17:18:50.000Z","uid":202698,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f8d5a2d513966d5b14cf709b7fc491b16323fc","tid":946615,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181217/photo/bkn-20181217214141817-1217_00842_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181217214141817-1217_00842_001_01p.jpg&h=e8eff95e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181217/bkn-20181217214141817-1217_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181217%2Fbkn-20181217214141817-1217_00842_001.html&d=jrtsyvjcMbw9rH99mlC5lLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=b6058bbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181217/bkn-20181217214141817-1217_00842_001.html</a><br />\n比特大陸官網上顯示，D3礦機僅售300元人幣。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n近日，內地登入全球第一大礦機廠商&mdash;&mdash;比特大陸(Bitmain)官網發現，曾經爆炒致上萬、乃至數萬元人民幣(下同)的礦機，一機難求，<span style=\"color: red;\">甚至要求助走私的各種虛擬貨幣掘礦機，都已大幅降價。與原年初定價相比，多款機型已降至低於一折，最低僅300元。</span><br />\n<br />\n其中比特幣礦機方面，T9+最為明顯。官網顯示，螞蟻礦機T9+10.5T （含APW7電源），<span style=\"color: red;\">單價1,800元。同時官網顯示，APW7電源單價650元，也就是螞蟻礦機T9+10.5T實際售價僅為1,150元。按現在的價格，這台礦機已經跌到年初的4.6%。</span><br />\n<br />\n在另一虛擬貨幣達世幣(Dash)礦機方面，D3掘礦機跌得同樣悽慘。官網顯示，螞蟻礦機D3 17G，單價為300元。達世幣誕生於2014年，與比特幣相比，具有匿名性更高、交易速度更快的特色。<br />\n<br />\n從去年初，達世幣價格從幾美元一路飆升到數百美元。去年8月，比特大陸正式推出達世幣礦機D3，當時官網標價11,300元，現在已跌至原價的2.7%，只剩原價的零頭。"},{"pid":"fa2ca4ff88e2219c5aaa71c34b5d631647a3fb2c","tid":946615,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不用怕只是技術調整.jpg"},{"pid":"01acbd88f932d69517a7cbc8ea4b8f09ee98f214","tid":946615,"uid":81518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"608b24be892eb46f83fc5db34d9da406d4d02f14","tid":946615,"uid":86097,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"daefa063414b21e1e1d635ec769bca382aad605d","tid":946615,"uid":139228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"礦機可唔可以用黎當電腦上網打機用"},{"pid":"56312a2a2614ecd6b4b4d561b7bb147fca8f37d5","tid":946615,"uid":210693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"幾舊水買舊爛鐵<br />\n<br />\n送都唔撚要啦傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998f6b94de2f7ad3d253734439f0c868c8704952","tid":946615,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daefa063414b21e1e1d635ec769bca382aad605d","tid":946615,"uid":139228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"礦機可唔可以用黎當電腦上網打機用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:21:41.000Z","msg":"個設計唔係俾你打機，無driver"},{"pid":"78efd5248269a8322d3d91a1d225ca996aef5288","tid":946615,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daefa063414b21e1e1d635ec769bca382aad605d","tid":946615,"uid":139228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"礦機可唔可以用黎當電腦上網打機用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9955d8431c7ee0008556ace8ff7fb63c9a46be39","tid":946615,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"Can it play GTA5@60FPS?"},{"pid":"3986de144d5e25cf3f905ec4c351cbf5c5d67c2f","tid":946615,"uid":15564,"like":1